# Chapter 11: Movie Recommendation System using K-Means Clustering

## Introduction

This project implements a Movie Recommendation System using K-Means Clustering, an unsupervised machine learning algorithm.

Movies are grouped based on similarity in rating and popularity, allowing recommendations without requiring labeled data.

---

# Problem Statement

Movie platforms contain thousands of movies.

Users often struggle to discover content matching their interests.

Goals:

* Group similar movies.
* Discover hidden patterns.
* Recommend similar movies.

---

